title: Ep. - 209 - REAL WORLD ALUM KELLEY WOLF AND SAY YES TO THE DRESS REVIEW
description:
Real World and Road Rules alum Kelley Wolf talks about Salt Lake City as the new Real Housewives franchise and gives concrete advice for holiday questions. Kelley is a Certified Life & Personal Development Coach and Speaker. 

 

The band Makuta created Kate’s theme song. She forced them to watch and review episodes of Say Yes to the Dress on TLC, which features the staff at Kleinfeld’s Bridal in New York City helping brides find their dream gowns.
